# Build-context excludes for the api/web production images. Keeps the context
# small and prevents host build artifacts from leaking into the image.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/coverage
**/reports
**/.stryker-tmp
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
# Never ship runtime secrets into the build context (the build stages run
# `COPY . .`). The committed template is kept.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
.git
.github
.husky
.vscode
.cursor
**/*.log
